# boothX

## Company blurb

boothX provides world first Tradeshow Performance Management platform. It allows marketers to manage the events, increase visibility for senior management and reduce cost upto 20%.

## Company size

5+ (as of January 2020)

## Remote status

Almost all of us are remote. We work across multiple cities in India. We have no future plan to change the current mode of working.

## Region

Current openings are for remote positions in Inida

## Company technologies

React, Firebase, AWS, Flutter

## Office locations

India

## How to apply

Check our jobs page: https://www.boothx.app/careers
